description:
Narasaki Naoto was born into a family of thieves. After committing marriage scam, he is arrested and taken to the upscale apartment of elite detective Oogaki Kaoru.

&quot;I became a detective in order to distort that pretty face of yours.&quot;

As the good-looking Kaoru with stalker tendencies calmly says this, Naoto slowly warms up to him as their peculiar living arrangement begins.
